{"tid":1475450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來呢啲就係大陸嘅後生仔","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:19:20.000Z","uid":296584,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a096870906ecbcdb5a2254e89ef6175810a6a1e","tid":1475450,"uid":296584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"近排我同左啲大陸人講近期嘅事 因為共產黨最怕就係果班人識諗嘢 我想可以話個真相比佢哋聽 但係其實佢哋有好多人都比呢啲假新聞誤導 佢哋由細到大都冇學過獨立思考 批判性思維 就算我哋講嘅嘢幾有point 幾咁啱都好 佢哋都係可以唔明<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>咁係因為垃圾中國政府啊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n培養左一班淨係識順從自己嘅人民 見到佢哋拎住啲假新聞同我講嘢真係好辛苦 見到咁多中國嘅後生仔比佢哋荼毒 但係又乜都做唔到 佢哋前世做咗啲乜 點解會投胎做咗中國人 見到佢哋咁樣真係好無奈 佢哋覺得而家生活安好 有飯食有屋住 就算啲法律啱唔啱佢哋都會去遵守 唔好搞到自己就得 <br />\n<br />\n根本同佢哋講幾多都唔會明 好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/15/211233_78a6cf2d3b7666dda958b380747760b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2F211233_78a6cf2d3b7666dda958b380747760b0.png&h=c51ccddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"023270219f60006d8ed5a0fd064ae31a230c6398","tid":1475450,"uid":296584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"晒鳩左我幾個鐘同佢解釋"},{"pid":"faeab8ba2c55b6685c449b04c2e9d0a5dad88406","tid":1475450,"uid":36702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"有啲人係被騙<br />\n<br />\n但有啲既得利益者  係甘願做豬 甘願為奴  你就算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba77f2ccecfb0733a5aceda3383a158a7fbdd56","tid":1475450,"uid":46906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"到燒埋身果陣就會<br />\n&ldquo;開始理解香港xxx...&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;國家連這樣的言論自由都沒有嗎？&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ce00d665b751c0f4a60beb4dc9a623c2d4a6d516","tid":1475450,"uid":260594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"佢哋係被訓練成唔關自己事唔好理，所以喺街度如果發生有人受傷/意外，其他人係唔理/ 就咁行過算"},{"pid":"81abc2991cb8c517350ca69fcf06d7da140370ce","tid":1475450,"uid":160102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"翻左場都係咁on9"},{"pid":"6d35ed310c59bfc75c66ca372f3b5dd319740b1f","tid":1475450,"uid":296584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔係唔知㗎喎 係扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"3e22cfa8ec82212abbed437b12c5bc76cef0ca88","tid":1475450,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxuKgX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxuKgX0.jpg&h=8d341078&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8949729ea008d3be5e37fa9bebc38af7f8587a0","tid":1475450,"uid":85694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"既得利益者點會破壞自己所得既利益<br />\n正等於你係有錢佬 你梗係屌鳩搞事既人<br />\n反正你有錢 去世界邊度都得<br />\n受苦個個又唔係你<br />\n公義可以當飯食架 買唔買到樓<br />\n唔好阻住我搵食 溝女就話之你<br />\n全世界人都一樣咁諗架啦<br />\n明既自然講兩句就明<br />\n唔明既有哂既定立場 得個嘈字"},{"pid":"1299ee0c66523def5cd3566d06404850846fce5a","tid":1475450,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e22cfa8ec82212abbed437b12c5bc76cef0ca88","tid":1475450,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxuKgX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxuKgX0.jpg&h=8d341078&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"不得了 叫佢上街示威啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好快變黑社會再坐三年"},{"pid":"bc4cb80e3f657ae11da2e60e5c0b2899a7586971","tid":1475450,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1299ee0c66523def5cd3566d06404850846fce5a","tid":1475450,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e22cfa8ec82212abbed437b12c5bc76cef0ca88","tid":1475450,"uid":2